title: Learnings
metaDescription: Research Synergy Foundation is a digital social enterprise platform that focuses on developing the Global Research Ecosystem towards outstanding global scholars. We build collaborative networks among researchers, lecturers, scholars, and practitioners globally for the realization of knowledge acceleration and to contribute more to society and humanity.

components.content: Research Synergy Institute is a learning platform to increase the productivity and capacity of researchers, facilitate collaborative research projects as well as developing effective knowledge dissemination.
